      <title>约翰·波德斯塔将取代约翰·克里成为美国最高气候外交官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/john-podesta-to-replace-kerry-as-top-us-climate-diplomat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统正在任命资深民主党战略家约翰·波德斯塔接替约翰·克里，担任在全球气候谈判中代表美国的最高外交官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/john-podesta-to-replace-kerry-as-top-us-climate-diplomat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示他“绝对”会阻止日美钢铁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/trump-says-he-will-absolutely-block-nippon-us-steel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党领跑者唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果他赢得 11 月大选，他将阻止新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的交易，强调这位前总统的经济民族主义可能会危及美国的外国投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/trump-says-he-will-absolutely-block-nippon-us-steel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 获得国际货币基金组织批准向阿根廷拨款 47 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/milei-wins-imf-approval-for-4-7-billion-argentina-disbursement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位直接知情人士透露，国际货币基金组织执行董事会批准向阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱政府拨款 47 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/milei-wins-imf-approval-for-4-7-billion-argentina-disbursement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷 Milei 计划与 Tinder 创始人举行技术峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/argentina-s-milei-plots-tech-summit-with-tinder-founder-amid-reform-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米雷 (Javier Milei) 周三与 Tinder 联合创始人肖恩·拉德 (Sean Rad) 进行了交谈，继续争取知名科技领袖的支持，同时国会议员就他最重要的立法优先事项展开辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/argentina-s-milei-plots-tech-summit-with-tinder-founder-amid-reform-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登官员同意权衡学生债务减免的变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/education-department-agrees-to-hold-another-student-debt-cancellation-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民主党议员和有影响力的倡导团体的压力下，美国教育部同意就替代学生债务减免计划的提议举行另一次规则制定会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/education-department-agrees-to-hold-another-student-debt-cancellation-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格在儿童安全参议院听证会上即兴道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/zuckerberg-offers-impromptu-apology-at-child-safety-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，在紧张的证词中，Meta Platforms Inc. 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 站在挤满人的参议院听证室前，直接向在社交媒体平台上遭受性剥削的儿童的家人道歉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/zuckerberg-offers-impromptu-apology-at-child-safety-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 及其首席执行官为支持加密货币的政客准备“战争基金”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/coinbase-coin-and-ceo-armstrong-prep-war-chest-for-pro-crypto-politicians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于布莱恩·阿姆斯特朗的两名最强大的竞争对手入狱或可能很快就会入狱，布莱恩·阿姆斯特朗无疑已成为数字资产行业最强大的领导者。他的崛起发生在一个有趣的时刻：美国大选竞选季开始，他的公司将其描述为“加密货币历史上最重要的一次”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/coinbase-coin-and-ceo-armstrong-prep-war-chest-for-pro-crypto-politicians</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员权衡以色列和乌克兰无边界要求的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/republican-senators-explore-stand-alone-ukraine-aid-in-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主要共和党参议员正在考虑放弃对新边境限制的要求，并支持针对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的独立紧急援助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/republican-senators-explore-stand-alone-ukraine-aid-in-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国挫败了中国针对路由器的黑客行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-disrupted-chinese-hacking-operation-that-targeted-routers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局和司法部官员周三表示，美国的一项行动破坏了中国政府支持的黑客攻击行动，其中间谍劫持了一个大型设备网络，以水利设施和电网等为目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-disrupted-chinese-hacking-operation-that-targeted-routers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta、X、TikTok 首席执行官因儿童网络安全问题遭到参议员批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，五个社交媒体平台的领导人因“未能”保护网上儿童免受性掠夺者和心理健康问题的侵害而受到美国立法者的警告，并被迫支持新的立法以实施控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
